{"tid":2457664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據報拜登政府或推出3萬億美元經濟發展計劃","createTime":"2021-03-22T23:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T00:58:52.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"217c879123a93f50d91af7fd61a5940f5b890e35","tid":2457664,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:18:59.000Z","msg":"據報拜登政府或推出3萬億美元經濟發展計劃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581993-20210323.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581993-20210323.htm&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=cfd5df65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581993-20210323.htm&h=f969923c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581993-20210323.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n傳媒報道，美國拜登政府據稱考慮推動達到3萬億美元的經濟發展計劃，涉及基建和加稅措施，納入成為長期經濟發展計畫，報道指出，有關計劃將於今個星期提交給拜登。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，基礎設施和應對氣候變化的措施，有可能成為這項計畫的關鍵部分，當中政府考慮在綠色項目方面，投入約4000億美元。另外，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">計劃亦涉及對人力資本的投資，包括降低少數族裔的學費，以及醫療保健計畫，另外亦會涉及用於育兒和長者護理方面的資金。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人拒絕發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3F24yAT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3F24yAT.jpg&h=ed194fee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc26652d7602fa2aafab5b21fdf45c9f22e78a95","tid":2457664,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美股又然"},{"pid":"90b384d5aa110194586fd6d4cdc7506e88c1c1da","tid":2457664,"uid":299187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:21:00.000Z","msg":"包唔包亞洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr